title: Amazing Spider-Man Vs The Kingpin (Sega Cd - 1993) Soundtrack
description:
The soundtrack from The Amazing Spider-Man Vs. The Kingpin game, released on Sega CD in 1993. 

This is not the same soundtrack as the Mega Drive/Genesis version or the Master System / Game Gear version, as the Sega CD version had an original musical score by Spencer Nilsen and the Mr. Big rock band.
